{
  "id": "RAW_904895ad",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-16）：耶鲁与谷歌 DeepMind 开发 C2S-Scale，突破 scRNA-seq 数据处理与分析新高度",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247499845&idx=1&sn=7da43d8d6dc4056f6427ca523127acdf",
  "date": "2025-10-16 10:22:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：C2S-Scale</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016162\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5185185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1150\" data-height=\"596\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0b8c3137&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwzjMGIq9cCcjyBQ7sO7H75TKQ2rrJ2SgUUQmselfRfYmoolBrNSR7fmFL6BRxzGJzZyuhDjXJcIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★C2S-Scale-Gemma-2-27B 是一个最先进的开放语言模型，基于 Gemma-2 27B 架构，专为单细胞生物学而微调。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过 Cell2Sentence (C2S) 框架开发，该模型将单细胞 RNA 测序 (scRNA-seq) 数据视为一种语言处理，能够将高维 scRNA-seq 表达数据转换为“细胞句子”——基因名称的有序序列，从而实现广泛的生物学分析。该项目由耶鲁大学、谷歌研究院和谷歌 DeepMind 合作开发，利用谷歌的 TPU v5s 进行训练，显著提升了模型的规模和能力，擅长细胞类型预测、组织分类和生成具有生物学意义的细胞表示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/c2s-scale\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/c2s-scale</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Coral NPU</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016165\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3851851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1148\" data-height=\"442\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50c47d65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwzjMGIq9cCcjyBQ7sO7H75BCQauPlNkkAGFtvknicTempPfmia2q3scpmmg4nKlWt6dyaJzN28flvw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Coral NPU 是由 Google Research 设计的开源硬件加速器，专为在边缘设备上实现能效优化的机器学习推理而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它是一种神经处理单元（NPU），也称为 AI 加速器或深度学习处理器，基于 32 位 RISC-V 指令集架构。Coral NPU 旨在集成到超低功耗的系统芯片（SoC）中，适用于可穿戴设备如听觉设备、增强现实眼镜和智能手表。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/coral-npu\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/coral-npu</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：UniPixel</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016166\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38333333333333336\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1148\" data-height=\"440\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=559dda87&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwzjMGIq9cCcjyBQ7sO7H75LuKJQ8VsvgZ5AZcb4lsWkzllhhREQ594w3gyEicQa9kwRUEdto9jXCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UniPixel是一个统一的多模态大模型，专注于像素级别的视觉-语言理解。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它灵活支持多种细粒度任务，包括图像/视频分割、区域理解以及一种新颖的PixelQA任务，该任务需要在视频中进行以对象为中心的指代、分割和问答。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unipixel\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unipixel</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：EgoAgent</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016164\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46574074074074073\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1152\" data-height=\"536\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6ee45d88&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwzjMGIq9cCcjyBQ7sO7H75iazd0AvTMGAWiaVjQamDD6SRNSxP3RJVOob8Gjg5ZJnbict8p78Rtv5Ag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EgoAgent是一个专注于自我中心视角世界的联合预测agent模型，旨在提升在自我中心视角下的预测能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目是ICCV 2025论文的官方实现，基于InternLM，一个开源的大语言模型训练框架。EgoAgent利用两个自我中心数据集，WalkingTours和Ego-Exo4D进行训练，提升模型在该领域的表现。项目提供了详细的环境设置和数据准备指南，支持在TriFinger模拟器中进行评估实验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/egoagent\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/egoagent</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Router-R1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016163\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4305555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" data-height=\"498\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83f2288c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwzjMGIq9cCcjyBQ7sO7H75bQWYDPdjWSzZSNbYiaPszabhlGho1du3qiaUwUhI4TVBSzYfrGEdmMgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Router-R1项目旨在通过增强学习技术教授大型语言模型（LLMs）进行多轮路由和聚合，核心是开发一种能够在多轮对话中有效路由和聚合信息的模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目已在NeurIPS'25会议上展示，并开源了模型权重和用于训练LLM路由器的数据集，旨在支持和加速社区内的相关研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/router-r1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/router-r1</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">⚙️ Robotics 开发</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Patch-as-Decodable Token (PaDT)</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016167\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6694444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1150\" data-height=\"770\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=040bc6fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwzjMGIq9cCcjyBQ7sO7H756d3jec4gff8flHhZ3YicicsTx9liaGMibHvPLVTf0xX6mDuDvZ3hdP7L9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Patch-as-Decodable-Token (PaDT) 是一种统一的多模态大语言模型（MLLMs）范式，能够直接生成文本和视觉输出。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">PaDT 的核心是视觉参考标记（VRTs），与传统的基于文本的边界框坐标不同，VRTs 允许模型通过视觉补丁直接表示视觉目标，从而实现更自然的视觉信息推理。通过引入 VRTs，PaDT 在 MLLM 的自动回归生成过程中实现了语义推理和对象特定的视觉标记预测。预测的视觉标记通过轻量级的 PaDT 解码器解码为低级输出，如定位或分割图。PaDT 在四个主要的视觉感知和理解任务中验证了其性能，均达到了最先进的水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/patch-as-decodable-token-padt\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/patch-as-decodable-token-padt</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文总结了耶鲁与谷歌 DeepMind 合作开发的 C2S-Scale 单细胞生物学 AI 模型，以及多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖多模态大模型、AI 硬件加速器和 Agent 等领域。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文总结了耶鲁与谷歌 DeepMind 合作开发的 C2S-Scale 单细胞生物学 AI 模型，以及多个前沿开源 AI 项目，涵盖多模态大模型、AI 硬件加速器和 Agent 等领域。",
  "summary": "本文以“今日开源”的形式，精炼介绍了六个前沿的开源 AI 项目。核心项目 C2S-Scale-Gemma-2-27B 由耶鲁大学、谷歌研究院和谷歌 DeepMind 合作开发，基于 Gemma-2 27B 架构，专为单细胞 RNA 测序数据处理和生物学分析微调，通过将高维 scRNA-seq 数据转换为“细胞句子”实现广泛的生物学分析。此外，文章还简要提及了 Google Research 设计的开源边缘 AI 硬件加速器 Coral NPU、专注于像素级视觉-语言理解的统一多模态大模型 UniPixel、提升自我中心视角预测能力的 Agent 模型 EgoAgent、用于 LLM 多轮路由和聚合的 Router-R1 项目，以及能够直接生成文本和视觉输出的统一多模态大语言模型 PaDT，这些项目共同展示了当前 AI 在生物、硬件、多模态、Agent 和机器人等领域的最新进展。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "C2S-Scale 模型利用大语言模型处理单细胞 RNA 测序数据，实现生物学分析新范式。",
      "explanation": "该模型将高维 scRNA-seq 数据转化为“细胞句子”，能高效进行细胞类型预测和组织分类，由耶鲁与谷歌 DeepMind 合作开发，代表了生物 AI 领域的重要进展。"
